  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うわ〜！
このパンすごくおいしい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wow〜! This bread is so yummy!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうだろう？
今回は、それで大目に見てはくれないか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Isn't it? 
Just this time, would you mind giving him a break?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うーん……わかったよ。
このパンお土産にすれば
きっとエミルも喜んでくれるし！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hmmm... Alright.
I'm sure Emil would be really happy
if I brought him this bread as a gift!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おい、お前！
俺のパンになにしてるんだ！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, you!
What the heck are you doing with my bread?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え？
なにって……携帯用のミソつけてるんだよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh?
What, you ask...
I'm adding some portable miso to it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>パンにミソ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Miso on bread...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おいしい！
このパン、とってもミソに合うね！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So yummy! This bread is so good with the miso!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>俺のパンに……ミソが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>My bread with... miso...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ショックなんだな、クーリッジ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Coolidge seems pretty shocked...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
